>> time required: 3 hours
>> course: condiment

Combine @garlic cloves{6}, @green chili{1}, peel of @lemon{0.5}, @olive oil{100%ml}.
Cover and cook on low heat until garlic is tender ~{20%minutes}
Remove from heat and let cool.
Strain oil and recover garlic cloves to put in oil.
Add juice of @lemon{0.5}
